casebody.data:
Shahla ZAR, Appellant,
v.
Nasser YAGHOOBZAR, Respondent. Motion No: 2018-597 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided September 18, 2018

(And a Related Proceeding)

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the consolidated action and proceeding within the meaning of the Constitution.
